mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "As I See It, by Bob Osgood", "Fashion Show Idea", "Overseas Dateline", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Keokuk Follow-Up", The Battle of the Square Dance", "National Convention News", "Discovery-New Square Dancers", "Style Series: Venus & Mars", "Herbert Lanks of Jenkintown, Pa.", "Round the Outside Ring", "Workshop", "Square Dancers' Guide", "On the Record", "Caller of the Month: Walt Swann", "Experimental: Chain Star Through" and "Roundancers: Tommy & Geneve Thomas".
